---
title: Peking Marinated Tofu with Sesame Rice & Aromatic Coconut Sauce
description: We love rice bowls because they’re so easy to customise with your favourite flavours. This veggie version uses Peking-style tofu, broccolini, carrot and ginger, with a drizzle of fragrant coconut sauce to tie the whole thing together.
